<sn><md>#### Decline of the Indus Civilization

The decline of the Indus Civilization began around `1500 BCE`. Scholars have not yet reached a definite conclusion regarding the exact cause of its collapse. It may have been destroyed by an invasion from external enemies, a devastating `earthquake`, or a catastrophic `flood`.

```id="o3r8vc"
